<br>
While I was leveling in the 50's, Rampage was explained to me as a static list of X number of players that consisted of the top aggro holders.  This list could not be changed save through deaths.  Recently I've been told that it is a changing list and will change based on the top aggro holders as they come and go.<br>
<br>
